Dan Saks and I posted some lists of C++ issues to the editorial
reflector last August, as  edit-36  and  edit-37 .  I re-formatted
these somewhat, and registered them with Josee Lajoie.  We jointly
decided that, at least for this initial posting, the abbreviated
format you see below would suffice for now.  When the issues lists
become more automated, I will format them into the (by now familiar)
"issues" format.

