Issue #core-313: clarify "shorter sequence" rules
__ _132p61b:
Suppose there's a conversion from A to B and from B to C, and functions







Mar  3 16:48 1993  Issues; by Plum+Saks; WG21/N0239; X3J16/93-0032 Page 28


